| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5271 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: cb8a2a39-a077-55f0-8bf2-f41d8ec3e2d5"
